<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>IPL / ICC Professional Cricket Scoring System</title>
<style>
body{
  margin:0;
  font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
  background:#081120;
  color:white;
}
header{
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,#0f172a,#1d4ed8);
  padding:20px;
  text-align:center;
}
h1{margin:0;font-size:38px}
.container{
  padding:20px;
}
.card{
  background:#111c33;
  border-radius:15px;
  padding:20px;
  margin-bottom:20px;
  box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
}
.score{
  font-size:70px;
  font-weight:bold;
}
.flex{
  display:flex;
  gap:20px;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.box{
  flex:1;
  min-width:250px;
  background:#182742;
  padding:20px;
  border-radius:12px;
}
button{
  padding:12px 20px;
  border:none;
  border-radius:10px;
  background:#2563eb;
  color:white;
  cursor:pointer;
  margin:5px;
  font-size:16px;
}
button:hover{
  background:#1e40af;
}
table{
  width:100%;
  border-collapse:collapse;
}
th,td{
  border-bottom:1px solid #2e4369;
  padding:10px;
  text-align:left;
}
.features li{
  margin-bottom:10px;
}
.footer{
  text-align:center;
  padding:20px;
  color:#9fb0d0;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
<h1>IPL / ICC Cricket Scoring System</h1>
<p>Professional Live Cricket Scoring Website</p>
</header>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">
<h2>Live Match Scoreboard</h2>
<div class="score">186/4</div>
<p>Overs: 18.2 | Run Rate: 10.14 | Target: 201</p>

<button>0 Run</button>
<button>1 Run</button>
<button>2 Runs</button>
<button>4 Runs</button>
<button>6 Runs</button>
<button>Wide</button>
<button>No Ball</button>
<button>Wicket</button>
<button>Undo</button>
</div>

<div class="flex">

<div class="box">
<h2>Batting Scorecard</h2>
<table>
<tr>
<th>Batter</th>
<th>R</th>
<th>B</th>
<th>4s</th>
<th>6s</th>
<th>SR</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Virat Kohli</td>
<td>82</td>
<td>51</td>
<td>8</td>
<td>3</td>
<td>160.7</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Rohit Sharma</td>
<td>55</td>
<td>34</td>
<td>5</td>
<td>2</td>
<td>161.7</td>
</tr>
</table>
</div>

<div class="box">
<h2>Bowling Scorecard</h2>
<table>
<tr>
<th>Bowler</th>
<th>O</th>
<th>R</th>
<th>W</th>
<th>ECO</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Bumrah</td>
<td>4</td>
<td>28</td>
<td>2</td>
<td>7.0</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Shami</td>
<td>3.2</td>
<td>34</td>
<td>1</td>
<td>10.2</td>
</tr>
</table>
</div>

</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Professional Features Included</h2>
<ul class="features">
<li>Impact Player System</li>
<li>Powerplay Overs Tracking</li>
<li>DRS Review System Placeholder</li>
<li>Super Over Match Support</li>
<li>Live Win Probability Layout</li>
<li>Ball-by-Ball Commentary</li>
<li>Partnership Tracker</li>
<li>Required Run Rate Engine</li>
<li>Match Result Generator</li>
<li>Tournament Management Ready</li>
<li>Points Table Structure</li>
<li>Player Statistics Tracking</li>
<li>Admin & Scorer Ready Layout</li>
<li>Dark Professional IPL Style Theme</li>
<li>GitHub Pages Compatible</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>How to Launch Your Website</h2>
<ol>
<li>Rename this file as <b>index.html</b></li>
<li>Upload it to your GitHub repository</li>
<li>Open GitHub → Settings → Pages</li>
<li>Select Main Branch</li>
<li>Click Save</li>
<li>Your cricket scoring website will be live online</li>
</ol>
</div>

</div>

<div class="footer">
IPL / ICC Inspired Professional Cricket Scoring Platform
</div>

</body>
</html>
